description:
The 𝓢𝓞𝓤𝓛𝓢 of TangleSwap are enigmatic, majestic creatures with a recently awakened interest in the IOTA & Shimmer universe. They bravely ventured into a long intergalactic journey through the tangleverse, and now they seek a place to call home. Their Shimmer home.
Keep in mind: 𝓢𝓞𝓤𝓛𝓢 are not for the faint-hearted; the only way to earn the loyalty and companionship of a 𝓢𝓞𝓤𝓛 is by merit, not by purchase. Throughout all of 2023, there will be multiple activities, events, and opportunities aboard the Tangleship to spot a wild 𝓢𝓞𝓤𝓛 and make it your best Shimmer partner.
Make sure to follow their journey across Twitter & Discord, and find out how to earn your 𝓢𝓞𝓤𝓛! 🎭 🛸
name: SOULS of TangleSwap
